{
  "texts": [
    "We attribute this failure to two factors.",
    "First, there is little room for errors in Hanabi.",
    "Any misplay leads to the loss of a life token.",
    "Second, Hanabi requires more complex Theory of Mind Reasoning compared to the Overcooked-AI environment.",
    "Each action requires agents to actively consider their partner's beliefs, intentions, and how they would react to implicit communication."
  ]
}